text: Sayid may refer to: * Sayid Mohammed, leader of a Dhulbahante anti-colonial state based in Taleh * Sayyid, a polite way of addressing a man in Islam * Sayyid dynasty, a 15th century Indian dynasty * Ahl al-Bayt Sayid, a descendant of the Muslim prophet Muhammad *Seydi, village in Iran
title: Sayid
